    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866300/extras/eac79923a97a88851ea9e3781f8e2b12.avif?t=1768580140\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866300/extras_big/eac79923a97a88851ea9e3781f8e2b12.avif?t=1768580140 width=800 height=150 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866300/extras/ebc89677f2eb51d5da5551e9334b7972.poster.avif?t=1768580140\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866300/extras/ebc89677f2eb51d5da5551e9334b7972.webm?t=1768580140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866300/extras/ebc89677f2eb51d5da5551e9334b7972.mp4?t=1768580140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将外星地界改造成繁荣的工业殖民地。在完全可摧毁的世界中采集资源，设计精细的生产线，实现效率最大化。你创造的每间工厂、每条管道以及每个哨站都会根据你的选择……和挑战而变化。<br><br>没错，会有传送带，很多很多的传送带。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866300/extras/63b2b3c32e8d942688c97bc561ec7703.avif?t=1768580140\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866300/extras_big/63b2b3c32e8d942688c97bc561ec7703.avif?t=1768580140 width=800 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866300/extras/38887eec179d1df19303191581304dfc.poster.avif?t=1768580140\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866300/extras/38887eec179d1df19303191581304dfc.webm?t=1768580140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866300/extras/38887eec179d1df19303191581304dfc.mp4?t=1768580140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个决定都会影响殖民地的未来走向，考验你在新疆土的恶劣环境中的领导力水平。另外，别忘了时刻供应充足的食物、住所和医药，保证源源不断的新定居者安居乐业。持续扩充的定居者和不断发展的工厂都有各自的需求，你能在二者之间保持平衡吗？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866300/extras/ff12b33667e3c2d9f9db26ba9cf2995b.avif?t=1768580140\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866300/extras_big/ff12b33667e3c2d9f9db26ba9cf2995b.avif?t=1768580140 width=800 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866300/extras/b294bf24b5ae26dac0494aed7806521b.poster.avif?t=1768580140\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866300/extras/b294bf24b5ae26dac0494aed7806521b.webm?t=1768580140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866300/extras/b294bf24b5ae26dac0494aed7806521b.mp4?t=1768580140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有足够的韧性，才能在恶劣的环境下生存。为了守护殖民地，你在平衡定居者需求的同时，还需对抗无尽的环境威胁和神秘的外星势力。战略规划和应变能力是确保生存的关键。</p>",
